Subject: Secunia Research: ClamAV Upack Processing Buffer
	Overflow	Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 14/04/2008

      - ClamAV Upack Processing Buffer Overflow Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
